{"tid":1467072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以諗返當初為乜而走出嚟？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:43.000Z","uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac6d2eb6454de9c74922250c0754bcf442c5da1","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我P牌 屌我係鬼先 我只係一個經常發夢嘅愛港普通學生 <br />\n大家走出嚟嘅目標到底係五大訴求定係為發洩？<br />\n我唔明點解大家要主動出手打人 <br />\n連救護人員都撞<br />\n唔明點解由和你飛變左阻你飛<br />\n唔明點解要主動向警車dum野<br />\n又話be water??<br />\n點解要放大自己比人拉嘅機會？<br />\n今日又<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再次目標不一致</span></span><br />\n處處都有自己友爆衝突<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拜託大家諗下背後有幾多人因為林鄭而犧牲</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">瞄準政權</span></span><br />\n知道大家好激動 見到popo好嬲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但麻煩大家忍下</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理智啲</span></span><br />\n如果做到我地乜違法行動都冇做 而黑警都照攻擊照拉我地的話<br />\n先比人見到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府係幾咁荒謬 黑警幾咁狗</span></span><br />\n前題係自己違法（非法聚會）都要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">be water</span></span>個隻<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">而唔係做d野搏比人拉</span><br />\nAnyway我唔係分化 你地做咩我都唔會割蓆<br />\n但我只係想大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">毋忘初衷</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好再掛住捉鬼</span><br />\n唔好再只係focus係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑警</span>度<br />\n諗下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">背後有幾多人已經犧牲左</span><br />\n我地 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一個都不能少</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化 <br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"9f27e8f6a0ed675fc11711861e832a8097786282","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拜託大家</span>"},{"pid":"158edce3a63d2f29a313b1dc06a1e775be64873e","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3101a9d6ce0d229a00425ab8468ab76dca96fcdf","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3bad19311fc2a369c2a89057bfb5618430725cf5","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"6b4c54e1f6390b7243ae2478ca436cb254387111","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"73775e31884f7232c0709c9a454d1434752c9bdd","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"3bd6cb6c97c15c8499ddfba04cb2ad1a708d106c","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a98e060de4a8a0282412121337b5c148244ec314","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"7acbd72a203b9240b0e3380142624946700f4823","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"256c0e84ee1d92b9389d6ed43997e2a0245ea2f5","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ddfc762a57f6261fdb5ccf48da1c9699b97a388f","tid":1467072,"uid":203180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"10"}]}